history.content:
Is there any way to enroll in classes with overlapping lectures? Next semester is my final semester at Cal and CS160 and 168 are the last two classes that I really wanted to take. The two have conflicting lectures on Thursdays, and from what I understand, the new system is prohibiting enrollment in cases like this. 

Is there a way to get around this or a way to make exceptions?
